movie.title: The Stronghold
movie.description_intro: The Stronghold is a Ukrainian adventure/fantasy film based on the same-name book. A present-day schoolboy Vit'ko goes a thousand years into past.
movie.description_full: The Stronghold is a Ukrainian adventure/fantasy film based on the same-name book. A present-day schoolboy Vit'ko goes a thousand years into past.

movies.title: Moving McAllister
movies.summary: Rick Robinson (Benjamin Gourley) is a ladder-climbing law intern from Miami with four days until the Bar Exam. Desperate to score points with his boss, Maxwell McAllister (Rutger Hauer), he commits to a favor he can't afford. He ends up in a rundown truck headed to Los Angeles, California with his boss' possessions, his Hollywood-bound niece, Michelle (Mila Kunis), and her pet pig. Amidst hitchhikers, breakdowns, and assorted local yokels, Rick finds love, life, and maybe himself in this trans-American road trip from Hell.

movies.title: Live and Let Die
movies.summary: Several British agents have been murdered and James Bond is sent to New Orleans, to investigate these mysterious deaths. Mr. Big comes to his knowledge, who is self-producing heroin. Along his journeys he meets Tee Hee who has a claw for a hand, Baron Samedi the voodoo master and Solitaire a tarot card reader. Bond must travel to New Orleans, and deep into the Bayou.

movies.title: Sumuru
movies.summary: Based on Sax Rohmer's cult novels "Sumuru", this futuristic fantasy takes you to an Earth-colony in the far future, in which women rule and men are used to propagate the race and work in the mines.

movies.title: Lone Wolf and Cub: White Heaven in Hell
movies.title_english: Lone Wolf and Cub: White Heaven in Hell
movies.title_long: Lone Wolf and Cub: White Heaven in Hell (1974)
movies.summary: The final film, and the final confrontation between Ogami and Retsudo. With most of his family already dead at Ogami's hands, Retsudo launches one last plot to destroy him, and when that fails, unleashes the fury of every remaining member of the Yagyu Clan.
